OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBenefit claimants to face  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmandatory work placements  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Benefit claimants who fail to find work
OL,6, for more than 18 months will have to   
OL,7, undertake work experience placements,  
OL,8, under rules planned for late next year.
OL,10,FIf they refuse they will lose access to
OL,11,Ftheir benefits for a period, the       
OL,12,Fgovernment says.                       
OL,14,FBut the charity, Mind, said the use of 
OL,15,Fsanctions would worsen peoples' mental 
OL,16,Fhealth.                                
OL,18,FIt is part of new plans to get people  
OL,19,Fback to work, which will also see an   
OL,20,Fextra #2.5bn spent on career support.  
